        START
        LDA     N
        STA     COUNT
        LDA     ONE
        STA     FACT

LOOP    LDA     FACT
        MUL     COUNT
        STA     FACT
        LDA     COUNT
        SUB     ONE
        STA     COUNT
        LDA     COUNT
        COMP    ZERO
        JGT     LOOP

        LDA     FACT
        STA     RESULT
        RSUB

N       WORD    5
ONE     WORD    1
ZERO    WORD    0
FACT    WORD    1
COUNT   WORD    0
RESULT  WORD    0
END